  "keyFeatures": [
    "Browser automation with Playwright and stealth mode for realistic traffic capture",
    "HAR (HTTP Archive) recording to capture all network requests",
    "AI-powered API client generation using Claude to analyze captured traffic",
    "Four operating modes: Manual, Engineer, Agent, and Collector",
    "Autonomous Agent mode with MCP-based browser automation, browser-use, and stagehand providers",
    "Multi-language output: Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript API clients",
    "Tag system for fine-grained control (@record-only, @codegen, @docs, @id)",
    "Claude Code plugin and Chrome Extension integrations",
    "Session history with cost tracking and token usage",
    "Multi-SDK support: Claude Agent SDK, OpenCode SDK, and GitHub Copilot SDK"
